SSH Client Configuration for key-based authentication

The 'Host *' block applies the following settings to all hosts

unless they are overridden by a more specific Host entry.

Host *
# Specify the path to the private key file.
# This fulfills the requirement to use the ~/.ssh/school key.
IdentityFile ~/.ssh/school

# Explicitly refuse password authentication.
# This fulfills the requirement to refuse authentication using a password.
PasswordAuthentication no

